    <div class="faq-a" id="how-much-does-ai-content-operations-cost-for-a-sma"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The tool stack costs $140 to $550 per month depending on which platforms you choose. The labor cost depends on whether you handle the work in-house or outsource parts of it. A solo marketer can run a basic AI content operations system for under $300 per month in tools. A three-person team with higher volume might spend $400 to $600 per month. The key is that the system replaces $2,000 to $3,000 in manual labor cost at typical freelance rates.</p></div></div>
