      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="can-one-person-run-an-ai-content-operations-system"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. A solo marketer with the right workflow and tools can produce 12 to 16 high-quality articles per month. That is the output level of a typical three-person content team without AI. The solo operator handles strategy, brief creation, AI drafting, editing, and publication. The key is a well-documented workflow and disciplined quality control. Our <a href="/blog/5x-content-output-ai/">5x content output guide</a> covers exactly how to scale production without adding headcount.</p></div></div>
  </div>
